/*
 * runtime_vars.h
 *
 * Runtime State Variables
 *
 * This file contains all runtime (non-calibration) global variables including:
 * - Engine state variables (RPM, load, temperature, etc.)
 * - Control state flags and timers
 * - Sensor readings and filtered values
 * - Learned/adaptive values (LEA_* prefix)
 * - Diagnostic state variables
 * - Communication buffers
 * - Ghidra-generated DAT_* variables (unknown/unnamed in disassembly)
 *
 * Organization:
 *   - DAT_* variables are Ghidra auto-generated names for unidentified data
 *   - LEA_* variables are learned/adaptive parameters stored in EEPROM
 *   - Named variables have been identified through analysis
 */

